creator: Hihub
descriptionHtml:
HiHub offers the best value for healthcare products, that enhance everyday life, contribute to your wellness and fitness.

From health to beauty and self-care to online doctor’s support. Now you can shop the healthcare products you need, and find professional support from top healthcare specialists all in one single APP.
HiHub offers a wide range of medications, healthcare supplements and vitamins that are hard to find, processes all orders from quality-controlled distribution centers.

Besides healthcare products, medication, vitamins, and supplements, HiHub offers doctor's services such as online consultation, helps to read the doctor's prescriptions, and find quick solutions for any health-related issue you might have at the moment. All modern health care solutions right in your hands: safe and handy.

With this Android app, you can shop for HiHub products from the convenience of your Android device. This app supports 3 languages (English, Armenian, Russian.) We ship products directly to the consumer in Armenia.
descriptionShort: HiHub offers the best value for healthcare products and services.
